```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer as Customer / Broker
    participant APEX as APEX
    participant AXA as AXA

    Customer->>APEX: Insurance Enquiry / Renewal Request

    Note over APEX: Risk Assessment
    APEX->>APEX: Collect CDD Information
    APEX->>APEX: Assess Risk
    APEX->>APEX: Check Authority Limits

    Note over APEX,AXA: Compliance Review
    APEX->>AXA: Submit Customer Information
    AXA->>AXA: Sanction Screening
    AXA->>AXA: Clash Checking
    AXA->>AXA: Due Diligence Review

    alt Cleared to Proceed
        AXA-->>APEX: Cleared

        opt Referral Risk
            APEX->>AXA: Submit Referral
            AXA-->>APEX: Approve / Decline
        end

        APEX->>Customer: Issue Quotation
        Customer->>APEX: Accept Quotation

        Note over APEX: Bind Risk Under Delegated Authority

        APEX->>AXA: Submit Policy Issuance Instruction
        AXA-->>APEX: Policy / Certificate Issued

        APEX->>Customer: Deliver Policy
    else Not Cleared
        AXA-->>APEX: Decline
        APEX-->>Customer: Notify Decline
    end
```
